title: Local Hour: All We Need Is A 3 And Out
description:
Stugotz tries to temper his expectations for the Jets and Zach Wilson, the Dolphins managing to lose despite outgaining the Vikings by nearly 2-1, everyone saying "Too Much Time" for Patrick Mahomes, and getting married on a Thursday.
